BATCH TRANSCRIPTION UPDATE

  The `spx batch transcription update` command updates an existing
  transcription request with a new name, description, or project association.

USAGE: spx batch transcription update [...]

  CONNECTION                      (see: spx help batch connection)
    --key KEY                     (see: spx help batch key)
    --region REGION               (see: spx help batch region)

  UPDATE
    --project URL                 (see: spx help batch transcription project)
    --name NAME                   (see: spx help batch transcription name)
    --description DESCRIPTION     (see: spx help batch transcription description)
    --transcription URL           (see: spx help batch transcription reference)

